text: Ani yunusako samudaya baheka kunai bastile imana lya'ena, jabaki imana lya'ebata tinala'i pha'ida hunthyo, ho (‘‘yunusako’’ kaumale) jaba imana lyayo ta hamile duniyamko jindagima tiniharubata tiraskarapurna sajaya hata'ihalyamai, ra eka avadhisam'ma sansarika labhaharu utha'une tiniharula'i avasara pradana garyaum
